Package: quantlab
Title: High-Speed Strategy Backtester
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Truong Giang", "Do",      email = "giangh14cqt@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jan",          "Melan",                                     role = "aut"),
    person("Sebastian",    "Chmielewski",                               role = "aut"))
Description: A high-speed backtesting framework combining R6 classes for
    stateful portfolio simulation, a formally validated S4 configuration
    layer, vectorized R signal generation, and a compiled Rcpp engine for
    path-dependent daily loops. Ships with a Shiny dashboard for interactive
    strategy exploration. Designed for Polish market data (stooq.pl format).
